Le Charles, [1934], in Lhomme, Catalogue des 
<normalizedToken id="75F44DCBDCF83F4C38559D2EC2D5D0A1" originalValue="Lépidoptères">Lepidopteres</normalizedToken>
de France et de Belgique 1: 683 (
<taxonomicName id="7179B250DE864BAB858C444DFF372623" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="126" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Zygaena</taxonomicName>
